      "body" : "About the 32 -> sizeof(vch) change... I agree that sizeof(vch) is cleaner, but if a change would be made that changes vch's size, things would break in more subtle ways (because the serialization of keys would differ).\r\n\r\nOne possibility is doing the 32 -> sizeof(vch), but also adding an asset/static_assert that sizeof(vch) == 32, with a comment explaining that this can't just be changed. That way you get both properties.",
